text: Charles O'Brien (19 May 1921 - 15 December 1980) was an Australian cricketer. He played one first-class matches for New South Wales in 1945/46. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1921 births Category:1980 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
